Reasoning: 
- cs.GT (Game Theory): The paper is primarily focused on mean field games, which are a type of game theory model. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses deep inverse reinforcement learning to learn MFG models from real data. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses machine learning techniques to model population behavior. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper applies MFG models to a real-world social media population. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses predicting the temporal evolution of population distributions, which is related to control theory.
